#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""hq — unified HQ CLI: task / mail / cal / drive / wiki / queue.

One entry point wrapping `gh` (GitHub Projects v2), `gws` (Google Workspace)
and `rg` (wiki search). Every command prints small, capped JSON to stdout and
exits nonzero with {"error": "..."} on failure. Run `hq --help` for the tree.
"""
